The PC version has been found to be missing lighting effects.

See below image... &lt;a href=&quot;
http://img705.imageshack.us/img705/4797/ssf4aelightingissues.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
